        _angular_core__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__["ɵɵtext"](192, " New bus lanes have reduced commuting time in Yichang. ADB invested to help construct almost 24 kilometers of dedicated lanes where clean, modern, and fast-moving buses could cut through gridlock. ");
