        _angular_core__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__["ɵɵtext"](162, " ADB continues to scale up support for gender equality and social inclusion (GESI) in South Asia. ADB promoted gender equality in 95% of its number of committed projects in South Asia during 2018\u20132020, up from 89% during 2017\u20132019. ");
