        _angular_core__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__["ɵɵtext"](164, "ADB committed $2.2 million for a regional transaction technical assistance facility to better integrate GESI in project design and implementation in its operations in the region. The facility will also strengthen the gender-equality capacities of executing and implementing agencies. ");
        _angular_core__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__["ɵɵelementEnd"]();
        _angular_core__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__["ɵɵelementStart"](165, "p");
        _angular_core__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__["ɵɵtext"](166, "In Bangladesh, ADB committed $50 million in additional financing to a microenterprise development project that will scale up gender-inclusive finance for microenterprises severely impacted by the COVID\u201119 pandemic. The project will provide loans to an additional 30,000 microenterprises, 70% of which are led by women. ");
