        _angular_core__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__["ɵɵtext"](193, "By 2020, a total of 162 reconstructed schools, including eight schools funded by the Japan Fund for Poverty Reduction, had been handed over to their school management committees. All schools have been reconstructed following strict building standards and specifications, feature the latest educational amenities, and are well-equipped to assist people with disabilities. ");
