        _angular_core__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__["ɵɵtext"](202, " Despite the shift in focus brought by COVID\u201119, ADB has remained committed to addressing climate change and disaster resilience in South Asia. Of the total number of projects committed in South Asia in 2020, 58% included climate mitigation or adaptation components (compared to 63% in 2019). Total climate financing amounted to $1.7 billion, from ADB\u2019s own resources. ");
